WHY: The current code accepts any input with no validation. This is a security and data integrity risk. The .cursorrules explicitly forbids any types.
9. Wire MQTT into All Services (WHERE: services/*/)

Add MQTT publish logic to the incident service (publish to jukwa/incidents/{id}/status on status change)
Add MQTT publish logic to the commitment service (publish to jukwa/baraza/{ward_id}/commitments on creation and state transitions)
