10. Seed Data and Ward Boundaries (WHERE: data/)

Create data/wards.geojson with Nairobi's 85 ward boundaries (source: IEBC/Kenya Open Data)
Create data/agencies.json with the 50 most relevant national and Nairobi County government agencies
